ly</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Seventh Shawl Frustrations</span><hr size=1> Well, at 178 skill in pottery I attempted to combine the Velium Powder (from the Runed Shell (Enduring Breath)) with some water in the pottery wheel and failed.  Not sure if it was because of the dreadful lag, bad luck or too low skill, but was frustrating none the less.  Does anyone else have tales of woe surrounding the Seventh Shawl (or an extra Runed Shell (Enduring Breath)) on Bristlebane?<br>
<br>
Quaras Shadowscythe<br>
Master Potter--grrr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaslethalo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>maslethalo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 116<br> <font color=#333399>(8/13/01 2:16:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4906.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.firstworld.net/~tgilmore/cat.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Seventh Shawl Frustrations</span><hr size=1> Just bad luck my friend.  Luckily the only failure I had was on the part of the two plat bars, the small piece of velium and the pattern.  I was pissed, cuase I thought I was gonna have to run over to CC.  But I just auction 50 pp for a small piece of velium, heh didn't take long.<br>
<br>
Anyway on final  combine I got shammy dex buff, took a swig from a shammy dex potion and got enchanter insight and boon of garou.  If you are trivial and fail after all this Verant is playing very nasty tricks on you.<br>
<br>
I was nervous as hell on the final combine. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulirisindinilal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lirisindinilal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>First Post!</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333399>(8/4/02 3:23:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4906.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Seventh Shawl Frustrations</span><hr size=1> I'm sorry about the failure on combines.  As a suggestion in case it hasn't occured to you yet - go into the bazaar and do a search for &quot;shell.&quot;  Skim down till you find the correct one.  There's usually all three types available - cloud, EB, and the necklace with 5 charges EB.  Granted, this is assuming you would rather spend the money on it instead of kill for it.<br>
<br>
Lirisindinilal Blackthorne<br>
53rd Cleric of Clan Morituri<br>
The Nameless<br>
