</CENTER><bgcolor=#000000></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uxendrix.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xendrix</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Druid of The Grove</span><br>  Posts: 643<br> <font color=#333399>(8/9/02 9:17:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4906.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Seventh Shawl Frustrations</span><hr size=1> I was 175-185 in all skills that are used before doing my combines.  I ended up using 2 shells, but that was my only failure spot.  I did use a geerlock item on all combines though.  If worse comes to worse and you do not want to finish it, just get an Obulous Death Shroud.  Had the shroud had the effect on it before I started this whole shawl business, I very well might have just kept one of the few that I sold in the past instead.&lt;G&gt;<br>
<br>
 <p>-Galipure Stormdancer<BR>Sun Clan of Warriors<BR>Solusek Ro<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uchenier.showPublicProfile?language=EN>chenier</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 69<br> <font color=#333399>(8/9/02 5:29:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4906.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.nhbzone.com/up4it/up4it_images/cupcake5.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Seventh Shawl Frustrations</span><hr size=1> I breezed through the 7th after doing the 6th 5 times...hate those damn sirens.<br>
<br>
I'm working on the 8th now and want to get that mana 3 neck item. 8th shawl (15% extended enchancement) + mana 3 item will make raid buffing niiiiice. But I would only wear the mana 3 item for buffing sessions and not general use. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulochrin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lochrin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333399>(8/14/02 1:47:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4906.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Seventh Shawl Frustrations</span><hr size=1> runed shells cost me 10pp each.,<br>
